{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"48da38c9-850b-4840-863a-7c85563444a4","content":"With MSTest 3.8.2 on .NET 9, here's the recommended pattern:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests\n{\n    private readonly TestContext _testContext;\n    private MyService _service;\n\n    // Constructor injection for TestContext (MSTest v3+)\n    public MyTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        _testContext = testContext;\n        // Synchronous initialization here\n    }\n\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task SetupAsync()\n    {\n        // Async initialization here\n        _service = await MyService.CreateAsync();\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void SyncTest()\n    {\n        _testContext.WriteLine(\"Running test...\");\n        Assert.IsNotNull(_service);\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public async Task AsyncTest()\n    {\n        var result = await _service.GetDataAsync();\n        Assert.IsNotNull(result);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- **Constructor** — inject `TestContext` as a parameter (no property setter needed in v3+). Use for sync setup.\n- **`[TestInitialize]`** — use an `async Task` method for any async setup. Runs before each test.\n- **`[ClassInitialize]`** — for one-time async setup shared across all tests in the class (must be `static`).\n- Avoid `async void` — always return `Task` from async init/test methods.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"49ee7c79-8c34-4654-8208-70c9475e7115","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is using MSTest 3.8.2 on .NET 9.0. In modern MSTest (v3+), `TestContext` can be injected via the constructor. They also want async initialization. Let me provide guidance.\n\nIn MSTest v3+:\n- `TestContext` can be injected via constructor parameter\n- For async initialization, implement `IAsyncInitialization` or use `[TestInitialize]` with an async method\n- Actually, the recommended pattern is to use constructor for sync init and `[TestInitialize]` for async init\n\nLet me give a clear, concise answer.","outputTokens":509,"requestId":"57E3:1BCD7:2EC57FF:319CE9B:6A0494D3"},"id":"ad731138-da11-45fe-94f6-1c6ec6778bf8","timestamp":"2026-05-13T15:12:33.342Z","parentId":"051dac24-869b-4838-8c79-b72e3826a9a9"}
